2.1 Core Innovation Thesis

The 5G Vault Drive replaces the traditional "dumb storage" model with a cognitive cyber-physical system that integrates:

```
[Fused Silica Medium] + [AI SoC] + [Quantum-Resistant Crypto] + [Self-Healing FS] = Sovereign Data
```

2.2 Key Differentiators

Feature Traditional Storage 5G Vault Drive
Lifespan 3-10 years 100+ years (theoretical 13.8B years)
Security Model Software encryption Hardware-enforced quantum-resistant crypto
Intelligence None Embedded AI for protection & optimization
Resilience Limited (shock, temp) Military-grade (EMP, radiation, physical)
Power Profile Constant draw Near-zero when idle, energy harvesting

