8. RISK ANALYSIS & MITIGATION

8.1 Technical Risks

```
Risk: Quantum computing advances faster than predicted
Mitigation: Crypto-agility architecture, field-upgradeable algorithms

Risk: Unknown silica degradation mechanisms
Mitigation: Multi-site accelerated aging, 10-year study program

Risk: AI model poisoning attacks
Mitigation: Federated learning with blockchain verification
```

8.2 Market Risks

```
Risk: Competitor achieves DNA storage first
Mitigation: Parallel R&D in molecular storage, acquisition strategy

Risk: Regulatory ban on unbreakable encryption
Mitigation: Jurisdictional flexibility, government partnership program

Risk: Economic downturn reduces IT spending
Mitigation: Focus on compliance-driven markets (finance, healthcare)
```

8.3 Execution Risks

```
Risk: Supply chain disruption for rare materials
Mitigation: 24-month inventory, multi-source agreements

Risk: Manufacturing yield below target
Mitigation: Redundant production lines, continuous process improvement

Risk: Key personnel loss
Mitigation: IP protection, deep bench development, acquisition strategy
```

